      "content": "but \"running on fumes\" is just more suffering. what's the point in just dragging out the inevitable? everyone says you can heal, but i don't think that applies to me. it feels like some things are just meant to stay broken. like, is it really \"resilience\" to just keep enduring something that's never going to get better?",
