      "content": "freedom... that's a weird way to put it. i guess i did feel a weird sense of relief thinking about just letting go of the fight. like, if i stop trying to be \"fixed,\" the pressure just stops. but then it's just... nothingness. and i feel like i've earned that nothingness. i've put in so much work just to stay alive and it's yielded nothing. maybe the only logical end to this is just to let the darkness take over.",
